{"tid":23071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"姦劫荃灣鳳姐 四眼淫賊容貌曝光","createTime":"2016-12-04T17:47:51.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T16:33:13.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1da7a2c068b44caeee0119870f597b9a743bb7b4","tid":23071,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T17:47:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161204/large/1480858730_59d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161204%2Flarge%2F1480858730_59d5.jpg&h=100aa1de&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n荃灣上周四發生姦劫鳳姐案，一名中年男子進入荃灣川龍街一樓一單位，亮刀指嚇34歲鳳姐，先綁起鳳姐強姦，再劫去1,600元及一部值5,500元手機逃去，警方經調查後將案件列行劫及強姦，交由荃灣警區重案組第一隊跟進。 <br />\n<br />\n重案組探員在現場深入調查後，終在其中一個閉路電視錄得其「賊相」，今日公開發相追緝涉案男子。警方稱，該名中國籍男子年約40歲，身高約1.68米，蓄短直黑髮，瘦身材，戴眼鏡，案發時身穿深色上衣、深色長褲、深色鞋及攜有一個啡色斜孭袋，他案發後懷疑在眾安街近沙咀道登上一輛的士逃去。 <br />\n<br />\n警方呼籲如有的士司機曾於案發後接載該名涉案男子，或任何人士如就以上案件有資料提供，可致電6101 0206或3661 2400與荃灣警區重案組第一隊聯絡。"},{"pid":"f2c06be67ce36e912a7f90bd9faa4ab8527f2804","tid":23071,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T17:48:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://image.fingerdaily.com/forum/201406/09/222512mdan5it56udj6a6w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.fingerdaily.com%2Fforum%2F201406%2F09%2F222512mdan5it56udj6a6w.jpg&h=b5eb5646&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea9ea22fa051d7e196213aa0c592d6d8cabfddf2","tid":23071,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:01:59.000Z","msg":"仲以為係之前youtube單野"},{"pid":"f88dc4a914bc82dff874a6c494a463d5796574a9","tid":23071,"uid":6192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T22:05:33.000Z","msg":"好蝗樣"},{"pid":"9d76f179bcff2a30ce184f86458c3d3874448e2b","tid":23071,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:14:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid